The paper deals with a fundamental problem in string matching, which is a topic in computer science that is closely related to data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), computational geometry (cs.CG), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of dimensionality reduction techniques also suggests a connection to machine learning and data analysis (cs.LG).
